name: Curtis Moe
description:
"The worst day of my life was when i went to my client's office to do a revision for their billboard campaign. The head of Marketing sat next to me, adjusting the size of the logo until it looks "perfect" to him. 
we sat there, getting back and forth for straight 5 fucking hours. 

I'm so sick of it so after a short break i showed him a preview from my first attempt and guess what.... 
this perfectionist mother fucker approved my first design....

dude if eating another alien is not a crime i would eat him for dinner" 


Quantity 1/20 

Rarity : Alienation first edition event pfp (1 of 4) / rare 

Benefits : Each holder will have a chance to join a raffle to get the rare ID of 
           Curtis Moe
